/code> scene, attach an <code>AudioStreamPlayer</code> node and a <code>TileMap</code> node. I went ahead and renamed the <code>AudioStreamPlayer</code> node to \"Jukebox\" and the <code>TileMap</code> node to \"DungeonMap\". Again, you can name these whatever you like but keep the names in mind when we reference them in the script.</li>\n<li>Finally, right click on the root Level node and attach a new script named <code>level.gd</code>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>At this point your setup should look like so:</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1915 1010' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-05167f42f4f315ebe52247d1d972b029'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-05167f42f4f315ebe52247d1d972b029)' width='1915' height='1010' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAAiCAYAAADvVd%2bPAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAGb0lEQVRo3uVZaXPbNhDVH/Eh674oSiIpUTx0U9RlW5bj2vHRZppOO00/dKbT37/dtxQlWpEde2KnUfzhDQASBPAeFgssGMspJuWVJpUqDhXKFik1lwqqtSpninXaT5TpgLF3pAiknFTpMFV5MvBNulAnpeqSqrepwsjWhpSuDKhQcclqjalca3Ed49ltbwLfY5xoK5XTKZnTCDx1s0%2blqkNqvklK3pR6Mat7RnnV5RdtSubrlMjW6ChTk5fpokmK1qcUPy8bIzLbc6q7x1Q1fTpKV6WTAxHjaThMqRRfDjKeRloVxLktDDJ4pt77Zn8p/L4Ir6zKe2EZ%2bXjp3rt0XmdONtWdGVkd8GtTvuzwZJrSfzzJ/TA/9BlzvfdMaMyz0GG0KVVoMnGLmi0m2vDJ7JyT1T2n1vCa2v4NdUa3nH9PhnMsjauNMZX0YQBtSIruM4ZbEDwvRRC%2bQ76oeZFnvgDtadaMnP75UvwT6dfpoXxGjdaplFveheRRp8LjUetjTn0aHN9Rd3xLg%2bktc5xSsebxRA6pXPdJt2c86R2KtbxLGp/ccqOn1B2%2bI7d/Rm1vQb3hBRWrXSpUe1Sq9fnjHgvjULrkUopTNGSwwpW6R3XDo4Yzoao7YYvpUZmt5ovQl4iWN%2bqgrWqDRWCLqwGcR1lvjkhrBmXkTXcq47A7Jzz%2bBc88j4Pbmyx%2bpf7kjrzZz6TZc9KcORmtBRkuc/Svuc6AYp3BnI7P7qg94A/tsRBBg6VaR/D7p38FH//4h65/%2bUQ3H/6S9MNvf3OnfTHTRKbKS4JNi1MxsQ3ArDcBc3/o3apOKjDVgyUOl1gtqUgeS6FqdMjtzZjDUJY1loBmTcQa8mqHMkqLsmX2PZziOSw%2bBhNquDMhXqkP