ls\"></noscript></p>\n<p>Alright so now we're in the <code>level.gd</code> script and we have a bit of work to do but I'll go over it thoroughly.</p>\n<p>First, let's start off by setting up the variables we'll need to export. These variables will be able to be changed in every instance of the script and it's what's going to make the levels unique.</p>\n<pre class=\"language-gd\"><code class=\"language-gd\">extends Node2D\n\n# The starting position of the player within the level. This could be a spawn point but </code></pre>\n"}}]}}},"context":{}}